The problem is that you have only one word in a capturing group and then you&#39;re repeating the group, thus, only the last occurrence will be placed in the capturing group. You need to put the one word in a non-capturing group and then put the X words in the capturing group.

Try something like this:

&lt;!-- language: lang-regex --&gt;

    ((?:\w+[ ]){2})(string)((?:[ ]\w+){2})

[Regex demo][1].

